nodes.text: Return of the Jedi Weekly 29 is the twenty-ninth issue of Return of the Jedi Weekly, the continuation of the Marvel Star Wars UK series.
This issue reprints part four of the story printed in the US as Star Wars 78, along with part two of Star Wars 12.
The title on this issue's cover, Jason Murdered, misspells the name of Wes Janson, who appears in the story.
